---
import SectionHeading from "../../components/SectionHeading.astro";
---
<section class="bg-white py-20">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="grid gap-12 lg:grid-cols-[1.05fr_0.95fr] lg:items-center">
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <SectionHeading
          eyebrow="Shot intelligence"
          title="Map beats to cinematic panels"
          description="Comic Storyboarder understands shot vocabulary, reading order, and camera movement. Import scripts, auto-suggest panels, then finesse the story visually without losing intent."
          containerClass="max-w-xl"
        />
        <ul class="grid gap-4 text-sm text-slate-600 sm:grid-cols-2">
          <li class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 p-4">
            <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-indigo-500">Shot presets</p>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-700">Wide, medium, close, OTS, and ensemble framing with angle and lens modifiers.</p>
          </li>
          <li class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 p-4">
            <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-indigo-500">Camera moves</p>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-700">Annotate pans, tilts, zooms, and dollies with arrows that show up in animatic previews.</p>
          </li>
          <li class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 p-4">
            <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-indigo-500">Beat planner</p>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-700">Send beats from Script Formatter or paste text to create suggested panels with estimated duration.</p>
          </li>
          <li class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 p-4">
            <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-indigo-500">Reading order</p>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-700">Toggle between LTR Western and RTL manga Z-paths. Number balloons automatically, then adjust manually.</p>
          </li>
        </ul>
        <div class="rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50/80 p-6 text-sm text-slate-700">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900">Dialogue that sticks the landing</h3>
          <p class="mt-3">
            Balloon tails snap to character anchors and keep spacing from panel edges. Font size adapts to text length while
            preserving typographic hierarchy so letterers and editors can trust the mockups.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="relative">
        <div class="absolute -left-6 top-6 h-16 w-16 rounded-full bg-indigo-200/40 blur-xl"></div>
        <div class="absolute -right-10 bottom-6 h-24 w-24 rounded-full bg-purple-200/40 blur-2xl"></div>
        <div class="relative space-y-6 rounded-[2rem] border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-xl shadow-indigo-200/40">
          <div class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 p-5">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-indigo-500">
              <span>Beat import</span>
              <span class="text-slate-500">Scene 03</span>
            </div>
            <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-slate-700">
              <strong>Beat 4:</strong> Hero confronts rival on rooftop. Wind howls.
            </p>
            <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 text-xs text-slate-600">
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                <span class="inline-flex h-6 w-6 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-indigo-500/10 text-indigo-600">
                  WS
                </span>
                <span>Wide establishing shot · 2.8s</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                <span class="inline-flex h-6 w-6 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-indigo-500/10 text-indigo-600">
                  MCU
                </span>
                <span>Medium close on hero · 1.6s · push in</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                <span class="inline-flex h-6 w-6 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-indigo-500/10 text-indigo-600">
                  CU
                </span>
                <span>Close on rival · 1.4s · dutch tilt</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 p-5">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-indigo-500">
              <span>Balloon layout</span>
              <span class="text-slate-500">Panel 2</span>
            </div>
            <ul class="mt-4 space-y-3 text-sm text-slate-700">
              <li class="rounded-xl border border-indigo-200 bg-white/80 p-4 shadow-sm">
                <div class="flex items-center justify-between text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-indigo-400">
                  <span>Hero</span>
                  <span>Auto-fit 94%</span>
                </div>
                <p class="mt-2">"You won't control the skyline any longer."</p>
              </li>
              <li class="rounded-xl border border-indigo-200 bg-white/80 p-4 shadow-sm">
                <div class="flex items-center justify-between text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-indigo-400">
                  <span>Rival</span>
                  <span>Auto-fit 87%</span>
                </div>
                <p class="mt-2">"Then catch me before the storm breaks."</p>
              </li>
              <li class="rounded-xl border border-purple-200 bg-white/80 p-4 shadow-sm">
                <div class="flex items-center justify-between text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-purple-400">
                  <span>SFX</span>
                  <span>WHOOSH</span>
                </div>
                <p class="mt-2 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.4em] text-purple-600">Wind gust arc applied</p>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
